[src:plug-elixir/plug-readme] When submitting a pull request you should not update the `CHANGELOG.md`.
[src:plug-elixir/plug-readme] If you are planning to contribute documentation, please check our best practices for writing documentation.
[src:plug-elixir/plug-readme] Finally, remember all interactions in our official spaces follow our Code of Conduct.
[src:plug-elixir/plug-readme] Security patches for the last four minor releases.
